(Yeah, but haven't you taken her inside somewhere?)

Prebon started getting ready for the battle, when he caught something 
out of the corner of his eye.

"The wolf! He can smell us! Slayer, when we start the battle in 3 
cycles you kill the wolf. Understand?"
______________________________________________________________________

Starscream

Starscream arrives at the scene and sees Drillbit tossed with runied 
things everywhere and and No Inferno to be seen. He lowered himself 
down to Drillbit.

"Come on. We don't need Inferno. I captured the other bot he was 
with. She'll know where Megatron is," he popped the top on his 
cockpit, "Come on, I'll take you back."
